The Trial Chamber of the Extraordinary Chamber in the Court of Cambodia (ECCC) will hear the testimony of a Witness (2-TCW-923) by video-link from the U.S. 
Due to the time difference the Chamber will sit from 8 a.m. to 10 a.m. for three mornings (Phnom Penh time) from 30, 31 March and 1 April 2015. 
The Chamber does not envisage further hearings on those days and Hearings on Civil Party suffering will be held on 2-3 April from 9 a.m.